first, make sure that both drc_robot_utils and sandia_hand_utils are under ROS_PACKAGE_PATHS, then

run

bdi_parser drc_robot_utils/raw/drc_skeleton_vX.cfg to generate drc_robot.urdf

install generated drc_robot.urdf as drc_robot_utils/urdf/drc_robot.urdf

then

rosrun xacro xacro.py drc_robot.model.xacro > drc_robot.model
copy drc_robot.model into the gazebo model database as [somewhere]/model/drc_robot/model.sdf
